The Kings , who got 19 points from Brian Grant and 14 from Bobby Hurley , did n't get any closer than 14 points until the final minute .
A season-high 37 points from Terry Mills and a flurry of 3-pointers down the stretch were n't enough to bring Detroit back against Boston , which got above .500 for the first time this season .
Dino Radja had 26 points and 12 rebounds at Boston Garden .
The Pistons made five 3-pointers in 1:07 to close a 110-100 deficit to 116-115 with six seconds remaining .
Dominique Wilkins , who had 18 points , then made two free throws for Boston with five seconds to go .
