Scottie Pippen did it all for Chicago , getting 35 points , nine rebounds , six assists and five steals while helping keep Charles Barkley in check in the second half .
Pippen 's 13-for-17 shooting helped the Bulls withstand a late surge to beat Phoenix and end the Suns ' four-game winning streak .
