The videos , along with books and audio cassettes , are part of a well-orchestrated propaganda campaign which is funded in part by money raised in the United States , Arab oil states and Europe .
It is designed to win over Palestinians , especially young ones , who have lost hope in PLO leader Yasser Arafat 's ability to deliver change .
