Rush said he was just happy to have ended his scoring slump .
`` When you 're not scoring you 've got to battle your way through it , '' he said .
`` Even though I 've not scored for a while , I 've had two or three disallowed when I did n't think I was offside but you 've got to accept that you will go through those spells . ''
Rush hopes he can replicate his League Cup heroics when Liverpool plays at Coventry on Saturday in the Premier League .
