The stock market also suffered from a big drop in computer stocks .
Several rounds of computerized sell programs worsened the losses .
Bonds fell after the National Association of Purchasing Managers said its index of manufacturing growth rose to 61.2 percent in November from 59.7 percent in the previous month .
