`` Of all the people of my acquaintance in acting , I miss -LRB- McQueen -RRB- more than anyone , '' Attenborough , 71 , says in an interview in the Dec. 4 Parade magazine .
`` If he had lived , as good as he was in pictures , I think Steve would have grown and become the new Tracy , perhaps , '' said Attenborough , who became close to McQueen while filming two adventure films , `` The Great Escape , '' and `` The Sand Pebbles . ''
