Nzo will hold talks with President Lee Teng-hui and Premier Lien Chan during his visit , the Foreign Ministry said in a statement .
Lee attended Mandela 's inauguration in May and offered South Africa U.S. dlrs 70 million in loans to help farmers and to help former anti-apartheid fighters find jobs .
