Anil Kumble -LRB- 52 -RRB- and Nayan Mongia -LRB- 44 -RRB- helped India push past the 500 mark against the Caribbeans , the fourth time they have done so against the visitors in 64 tests .
Carl Hooper , who took five wickets for 116 , was the most successful West Indian bowler .
Swedish divers on Friday planned to survey the wreck of the sunken ferry Estonia , a Baltic Sea tomb for an estimated 800 victims of the tragedy .
The divers , making the first human surveillance of the wreck , intend to scrutizine the condition of the ship , which is resting on its side in 56-84 meters -LRB- 180-280 feet -RRB- of water off Finland 's southwestern coast , the news agency TT reported .
`` The weather conditions are good .
The weather wo n't hinder the work , '' Swedish maritime administration spokesman Lars-Goeran Bronow told TT .
The divers are to gather evidence to help authorities decide the feasibility of retreiving the bodies or taking some other action to preserve them .
More than 800 bodies are believed entombed in the wreck , although officials have said they may never know the exact number because of unreliable passenger lists .
According to the latest official count , 136 people survived and 913 died .
Only 94 bodies have bee recovered .
