`` I can be beaten but it will take a lot of hard work , '' said the Pakistani .
Eyles took 54 minutes to beat the sixth-ranked Walker 15-13 , 10-15 , 15-12 , 15-9 .
Eyles can take comfort from being one of the few men to have beaten Khan .
The Australian pulled off a remarkable victory at the 1993 Portuguese Open coming from two games behind and two match balls down to win .
