But international efforts toward lasting peace have failed over what seemed to be irreconcilable differences .
This is the first accord between the foes since they agreed March 29 on a formal cease-fire to end their 1991 war .
Seattle Seahawks running back Chris Warren was arrested after a car he was driving crashed into a utility pole , injuring him and two teammates .
One of the teammates , defensive tackle Michael Frier , suffered a serious neck injury , and is largely paralyzed , a doctor said .
